ster.com%2Fall-together-now-tickets%2Fartist%2F1649419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-national-and-jorja-smith-lead-first-50-names-for-irelands-all-together-now-festival-2024-buy-tickets-3598005">2024 年音乐节</a>于 8 月 1 日至 4 日举行，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国家乐队 (The National</a> )、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">乔雅·史密斯 (Jorja Smith)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roisin-murphy">罗伊辛·墨菲 (Róisín Murphy)</a>都有表演。 </p><p><iframe title="与 Fontaines D.C. 的 Grian Chatten 相处融洽：“我们的个性比我们发出的声音更重要”" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cAncWquXDE8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>出席此次活动的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future-islands">Future Island</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-vincent-mcmorrow">James Vincent McMorrow</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slowdive">Slowdive</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/natasha-bedingfield">Natasha Bedingfield</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/maribou-state-kingdom-in-colour-review-2373341">Maribou State</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-cant-swim">Barry Can&#39;t Swim</a> 。</p><p>对于 2025 年的头号人物 Fontaines DC 来说，该节目是该乐队计划明年举办的一系列繁忙现场表演中的最新一场。九月，他们宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-massive-2025-manchester-show-at-wythenshawe-park-3797642">在曼彻斯特威森肖公园举办一场大型演出</a>——在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>和英语老师的支持下——随后又传来了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-add-huge-cardiff-castle-show-to-summer-2025-uk-tour-plans-3806310">卡迪夫城堡举行大型演出</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-announce-2025-us-headli